Underlying source licenses still apply to their respective portions of
the data. See README.md § License for details. In summary:

  - U.S. Census Bureau data: public domain (17 U.S.C. § 105).
  - U.S. Postal Service ZIP assignments: not subject to copyright.
  - SimpleMaps US Zip Codes Basic: CC BY 4.0
    (https://simplemaps.com/data/us-zips).
  - IANA tz database: public domain.

The structure, normalization, and combination of these sources into
this single CSV is what Ready APIs releases under CC BY 4.0.
